rom\": 219, \"to\": 242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hannah Mckay/REUTERS MANILA, Philippines -Carlos Yuloended his scintillating Paris Games run with another historic feat.\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 366, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 245, \"end\": 257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hannah_McKay\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hannah Mckay\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hannah_McKay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hannah_McKay\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his scintillating Paris Games\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 333}, {\"ngram\": \"another historic feat\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 364}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo became the Philippines' first double Olympic gold medalist after reigning in the men's artistic gymnastics vault final at the Bercy Arena on Sunday, August 4.\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 384, \"end\": 395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.999999974902494, \"rank\": 2.509712986189844e-08, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yulo\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 372}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's artistic gymnastics vault\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 485}, {\"ngram\": \"the Bercy Arena\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Riding on the momentum of his golden performance infloor exercise, the 24-year-old Yulo averaged 15.116 points to claim the top prize as he sent the country to a frenzied celebration for the second straight night.\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the momentum\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 555}, {\"ngram\": \"his golden performance infloor exercise\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"the 24-year-old Yulo\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 620}, {\"ngram\": \"15.116 points\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 643}, {\"ngram\": \"the top prize\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"a frenzied celebration\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"the second straight night\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo impressed with his first vault and netted 15.433 points then garnered 14.800 points in his second vault, finally getting the job done after placing fourth in the same apparatus in theTokyo Gamesthree years ago.\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yulo\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 752}, {\"ngram\": \"his first vault\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 783}, {\"ngram\": \"15.433 points\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"14.800 points\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"his second vault\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 856}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"the same apparatus\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"theTokyo Gamesthree\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite his stellar routine, Yulo remained in danger of being overtaken as the rest of the field included former world champion and Tokyo silver medalist Artur Davtyan of Armenia.\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.939827401669641e-42, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}, {\"begin\": 1097, \"end\": 1102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999540705, \"rank\": 4.6075530122019566e-11, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\